title: the last summer
description:
After 8 years of friendship through high school and college, Chris, Matt, Colin and Seth have found themselves at the beginning of their last summer together. Before joining the real world, they've decided to make their final summer the most memorable thus far. How will this effect their personal lives, decisions and ultimately their friendship?

Folder does include extras: bloopers, music videos, trailers, photo gallery, deleted scenes and the sexiest moments of the last summer
